data.description: This pristine light filled upper level condo is located in the highly coveted Village Green. The Village Green is 68 acres of lush grounds; an oasis tucked into the neighborhoods of beautiful Baldwin Hills. Centrally located to all of Los Angeles, walking distance to the metro, and minutes from downtown Culver City. This second story condo has two large balconies, one off the front side and one off the back, offering gorgeous views of the park from each side! Some of the many features included in this meticulously restored mid century modern unit are refinished hardwood floors, designer lighting fixtures, water filtration system, washer and dryer in unit, remote controlled ceiling fans, a well maintained 1 car automatic garage with additional storage, and a large gated exposed-brick patio with brand new landscaping. A gardeners absolute dream home. The Village Green is a National Historic Landmark, has 24 security, an on site maintenance crew, and community events throughout the year.
